                     <interp inst="t18210411-174-person1707" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer, I was coming along, and Howie gave the prisoners in my charge.</p>
               <p>MELLIS'S Defence. I am innocent.</p>
               <p>HAWKINS'S Defence. I have only a father, and he is in the poor-house.</p>
